equation: homotopy(smooth(0, if driver.gain.y > driver.limiter1.uMax then driver.limiter1.uMax else if driver.gain.y < driver.limiter1.uMin then driver.limiter1.uMin else driver.gain.y), driver.gain.y)
homotopy(smooth(0, if add.u2 > eleDrive.limTau.yH then eleDrive.limTau.yH else if add.u2 < eleDrive.limTau.yL then eleDrive.limTau.yL else add.u2), add.u2)
homotopy(smooth(0, if driver.gain.y > driver.limBrak.uMax then driver.limBrak.uMax else if driver.gain.y < driver.limBrak.uMin then driver.limBrak.uMin else driver.gain.y), driver.gain.y)
homotopy(smooth(0, if driver.gain.y > driver.limAcc.uMax then driver.limAcc.uMax else if driver.gain.y < driver.limAcc.uMin then driver.limAcc.uMin else driver.gain.y), driver.gain.y)
$PRE.dragF.mode == 0 and (dragF.sa > dragF.A or $PRE.dragF.startForward and dragF.sa > dragF.A) or $PRE.dragF.mode == -1 and dragF.v > dragF.v_small or dragF.v > 0.0
$PRE.dragF.mode == 0 and (dragF.sa < (-dragF.A) or $PRE.dragF.startBackward and dragF.sa < (-dragF.A)) or $PRE.dragF.mode == 1 and dragF.v < (-dragF.v_small) or dragF.v < 0.0
not ($PRE.dragF.mode == 1 or dragF.startForward or $PRE.dragF.mode == -1 or dragF.startBackward)

(if dragF.locked then dragF.sa else dragF.A * (if dragF.startForward then Modelica.Math.tempInterpol1(dragF.v, {{0.0, 1.0}}, 2) else if dragF.startBackward then -Modelica.Math.tempInterpol1(-dragF.v, {{0.0, 1.0}}, 2) else if $PRE.dragF.mode == 1 then Modelica.Math.tempInterpol1(dragF.v, {{0.0, 1.0}}, 2) else -Modelica.Math.tempInterpol1(-dragF.v, {{0.0, 1.0}}, 2))) + dragF.B * dragF.v ^ 2.0 * dragF.Sign

info.file: D:/Centurion University/4th Semester/System Integration with DYMOLA/Dymola_Project/Project_habib.mo

equation: if dragF.locked then 0.0 else if dragF.startForward then dragF.sa - dragF.A else if dragF.startBackward then dragF.sa + dragF.A else if $PRE.dragF.mode == 1 then dragF.sa - dragF.A else dragF.sa + dragF.A
homotopy(smooth(0, if add.y > cutNeg.uMax then cutNeg.uMax else if add.y < cutNeg.uMin then cutNeg.uMin else add.y), add.y)

if ($PRE.dragF.mode == 1 or $PRE.dragF.mode == 2 or dragF.startForward) and dragF.v > 0.0 then 1 else if ($PRE.dragF.mode == -1 or $PRE.dragF.mode == 2 or dragF.startBackward) and dragF.v < 0.0 then -1 else 0
assert(cutNeg.uMax >= cutNeg.uMin, "Limiter: Limits must be consistent. However, uMax (=" + String(cutNeg.uMax, 6, 0, true) + ") < uMin (=" + String(cutNeg.uMin, 6, 0, true) + ")");
assert(batt1.SOCInit <= batt1.SOCMax, "SOCInit(=" + String(batt1.SOCInit, 6, 0, true) + ") must be smaller than, or equal to SOCMax(=" + String(batt1.SOCMax, 6, 0, true) + ")");

info.file: D:/Centurion University/4th Semester/System Integration with DYMOLA/Dymola_Project/Project_habib.mo
